    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Those who study and write about perceptible beauty in art and nature, together with the intellectual and emotional responses to beauty.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
